  "body": "ingress paths should be a list in the values file like this:\r\n\r\n```\r\ningress:\r\n  enabled: false\r\n  annotations: {}\r\n    # kubernetes.io/ingress.class: nginx\r\n    # kubernetes.io/tls-acme: \"true\"\r\n  paths: []\r\n  hosts:\r\n    - chart-example.local\r\n  tls: []\r\n  #  - secretName: chart-example-tls\r\n  #    hosts:\r\n  #      - chart-example.local\r\n``` \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nand then in the ingress template something like this:\r\n\r\n```\r\n{{- $ingressPaths := .Values.ingress.paths -}}\r\n...\r\n...\r\n.\r\n.\r\n.\r\n  rules:\r\n  {{- range .Values.ingress.hosts }}\r\n    - host: {{ . | quote }}\r\n      http:\r\n        paths:\r\n        {{- range $ingressPaths }}\r\n          - path: {{ . | quote }}\r\n            backend:\r\n              serviceName: {{ $fullName }}\r\n              servicePort: http\r\n        {{- end }}\r\n  {{- end }}\r\n```\r\n\r\nnotice i added an 's'\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
